rows.label: campfev11_550_100_msg0001
rows.name:
We must hurry to the court of the
Iiran King to make known Metsu's
foul intent.

rows.label: campfev11_550_100_msg0003
rows.name:
The sooner we can deliver our report,
the more chance we have of averting
the carnage that Metsu hopes to bring.

rows.label: campfev11_550_100_msg0004
rows.name:
Maybe it's best if I wait out the
front of the palace.

rows.label: campfev11_550_100_msg0005
rows.name: I've got a bad feeling about this.

rows.label: campfev11_550_100_msg0007
rows.name:
Actually... You guys'll be fine. Don't
pay too much attention to my weird
hunches.
